## Core types location

All shared types live in `src/types/`:

| File              | Contains                                                          |
| ----------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `sections.ts`     | `AnySectionT`, `CoreSection`, all section types (`*SectionT`)    |
| `wordpress.ts`    | `WpImage`, `WpAcfLink`, `WpPage`, `WpPost`, rest shapes          |
| `testimonials.ts` | `TestimonialDocument`                                             |
| `forms.ts`        | `CF7FormDefinition`                                               |
| `globals.ts`      | `GlobalSettings` (header/footer globals)                          |
| `acf.ts`          | Raw ACF REST shapes                                               |
| `seo.ts`          | Yoast-derived SEO types                                           |

