## CoreSection

Every section type extends `CoreSection`:

```ts
export type CoreSection = { _key: string; id: string };
```

- `_key` — ACF flexible content row key (stable across saves); used as React `key` fallback.
- `id` — UUID generated at normalization time by `newSectionId()`.

Sections are defined as intersections:
```ts
export type MySectionT = CoreSection & {
  type: "my_section";
  // ... fields
};
```

