## Type naming convention

| Thing                 | Convention                    | Example                        |
| --------------------- | ----------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Section type          | PascalCase + `SectionT`       | `AudiencePromoCardSectionT`    |
| Section type literal  | snake_case                    | `"audience_promo_card"`        |
| Sub-item type         | PascalCase + descriptive name | `AudiencePromoCardFeatureRowT` |
| Enum-style literal    | PascalCase + `T`              | `WhoWeAreForItemAccentT`       |
| WordPress REST shapes | PascalCase starting with `Wp` | `WpImage`, `WpAcfLink`         |

