## WpImage and WpAcfLink

```ts
// From src/types/wordpress.ts
type WpImage = {
  url: string;
  alt: string;
  id?: number;
  title?: string;
  width?: number;
  height?: number;
  sizes?: Record<string, unknown>;
};

type WpAcfLink = {
  title?: string;
  url: string;
  target?: string;
};
```

- `WpImage` is produced by `asImage()` in `field-mappers.ts` — never construct it manually.
- `WpAcfLink` is produced by `asLink()` — never construct it manually.
- Both may be `null`; always check before use.

---

## CtaItem

```ts
export type CtaItem = { text: string; url: WpAcfLink | null };
```

Produced in batches by `mapCtaRepeater()`. Used in nearly every section that has a CTA button.

